 :tx/rationale "Create task: ACP-15: CommandOutput extension — add optional ActionProjection field for incremental migration (INV-BUDGET-007). BACKGROUND: AUDIT ISSUE 2. The current run() function returns Result<CommandOutput, BraidError>. ACP needs to thread ActionProjection through the pipeline without changing every command at once. Solution: add an optional projection field to CommandOutput itself: pub projection: Option<ActionProjection>. Commands that adopt ACP set this field; legacy commands leave it as None. The project_output() gate (ACP-8) checks this field: if Some, uses ACP rendering; if None, falls back to enforce_ceiling(). This enables INCREMENTAL MIGRATION — each command converts independently, and legacy commands continue working exactly as before. APPROACH: (1) Add pub projection: Option<ActionProjection> to CommandOutput. (2) Add CommandOutput::with_projection(projection) builder method. (3) Update CommandOutput::from_human() to set projection=None. (4) Update render() to prefer projection rendering when available and mode != Json (JSON always includes both projection and raw json field). Tests: (A) CommandOutput without projection renders identically to current behavior. (B) CommandOutput with projection renders projection at agent budget. (C) from_human() has projection=None. FILE: crates/braid/src/output.rs"
